<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-white" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 3: Articoli e pronomi -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</span>
      <span>Leggi il testo seguente e osserva le parole evidenziate: alcune sono articoli, altri pronomi. Completa la tabella.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-4 text-gray-700 bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
      <p>"<strong>Il</strong> papà prepara per Mattia e i suoi amici <strong>una</strong> focaccia. Quando è cotta, <strong>la</strong> toglie dal forno e <strong>la</strong> taglia a fette; poi prende tutte <strong>le</strong> parti e <strong>le</strong> mette in <strong>un</strong> contenitore perché Mattia porti <strong>la</strong> focaccia è al parco per merenda."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <% [
        { word: "Il", num: 1, articolo: true },
        { word: "una", num: 2, articolo: true },
        { word: "la", num: 3, articolo: false },
        { word: "la", num: 4, articolo: false },
        { word: "le", num: 5, articolo: true },
        { word: "le", num: 6, articolo: false },
        { word: "un", num: 7, articolo: true },
        { word: "la", num: 8, articolo: true }
      ].each do |item| %>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong><%= item[:word] %></strong> (<%= item[:num] %>)</span>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="word<%= item[:num] %>" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="<%= item[:articolo] %>" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>Articolo</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="word<%= item[:num] %>" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="<%= !item[:articolo] %>" class="w-5 h-5">
              <span>Pronome</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 4: Aggettivi qualificativi -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</span>
      <span>Quale dei seguenti gruppi di aggettivi contiene solo aggettivi qualificativi?</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="aggettivi" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">alto • buono • molto • simpatico</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="aggettivi" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">splendido • vostro • difficile • profumato</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="aggettivi" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">leggero • interessante • questo • umido</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="aggettivi" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="true" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">superficiale • fresco • liscio • liquido</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 5: Pronome relativo e preposizione -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</span>
      <span>Inserisci tra le due frasi un pronome relativo e una preposizione adatti.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• La persona</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="a cui" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">ti ho parlato è arrivata.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 6: Poco come avverbio -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</span>
      <span>In quale delle seguenti frasi <strong class="underline text-blue-600">poco</strong> è un avverbio?</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="poco" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Mangia quel poco che è rimasto.</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="poco" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="true" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">A pranzo ho mangiato poco.</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="poco" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Mi accontento di poco.</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="poco" data-multiple-choice-target="answer" data-correct-answer="false" class="w-5 h-5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Metti poco zucchero, mi raccomando.</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 7: Congiunzione -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold">7</span>
      <span>Collega le due frasi con una congiunzione adatta.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Il cane si stava avviando verso la casa</span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 px-2 py-1 w-24" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="quando" placeholder="">
        <span class="text-gray-700">qualcuno lo chiamò.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer with reference -->
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold">Grammatica - Ripasso generale</p>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
